question: $\frac{x^{2}-2x\sqrt{3}-\sqrt[3]{4}+3}{x-\sqrt{3}}$ ифоданинг $x=\sqrt{3}-\sqrt[3]{2}$ бўлгандаги қийматини топинг.
output:
$x=\sqrt{3}-\sqrt[3]{2}$ бўлганда, $\frac{x^{2}-2x\sqrt{3}-\sqrt[3]{4}+3}{x-\sqrt{3}}$ ифодаси:

\begin{align*}
\frac{x^{2}-2x\sqrt{3}-\sqrt[3]{4}+3}{x-\sqrt{3}}&=\frac{(\sqrt{3}-\sqrt[3]{2})^{2}-2(\sqrt{3}-\sqrt[3]{2})\sqrt{3}-\sqrt[3]{4}+3}{\sqrt{3}-\sqrt[3]{2}-\sqrt{3}}\\
&=\frac{3-2\sqrt{3}\sqrt[3]{2}+\sqrt[3]{4}-2\sqrt{3}+2\sqrt[3]{2}\sqrt{3}-\sqrt[3]{4}+3}{-\sqrt[3]{2}}\\
&=\frac{6-2\sqrt{3}\sqrt[3]{2}+2\sqrt[3]{2}\sqrt{3}}{-\sqrt[3]{2}}\\
&=\frac{6-2\sqrt{3}(\sqrt[3]{2}-\sqrt[3]{2})}{-\sqrt[3]{2}}\\
&=\frac{6}{-\sqrt[3]{2}}\\
&=\boxed{-\sqrt[3]{2}^{2}}\\
&=\boxed{-\sqrt[3]{4}}
\end{align*}

D) $\sqrt[3]{2}$.

output:
Бул масалада, $1-\sin ^{6}22.5^\circ+\cos ^{6}22.5^\circ$ ni hisoblash uchun, biz quyidagi qoidalarni qayta yozishimiz mumkin:

\anza{align*}
\sin ^{2}22.5^\circ+\cos ^{2}22.5^\circ&=1\\
\sin ^{2}22.5^\circ&=\cos ^{2}67.5^\circ\\
\cos ^{2}22.5^\circ&=\sin ^{2}67.5^\circ
\end{align*}Shuning uchun, biz quyidagilarni yozishimiz mumkin:

\anza{align*}
1-\sin ^{6}22.5^\circ+\cos ^{6}22.5^\circ&=1-\sin ^{6}22.5^\circ+\cos ^{6}22.5^\circ\\
&=1-\sin ^{3}22.5^\circ\cos ^{3}22.5^\circ\left(\frac{1}{\sin ^{3}22.5^\circ}+\frac{1}{\cos ^{3}22.5^\circ}\right)\\
&=1-\sin ^{3}22.5^\circ\cos ^{3}22.5^\circ\left(\frac{\sin ^{3}67.5^\circ+\cos ^{3}67.5^\circ}{\sin ^{3}22.5^\circ\cos ^{3}22.5^\circ}\right)\\
&=1-\sin ^{3}22.5^\circ\cos ^{3}22.5^\circ\left(\frac{(\sin ^{2}67.5^\circ+\cos ^{2}67.5^\circ)(\sin 67.5^\circ+\cos 67.5^\circ)}{\sin ^{3}22.5^\circ\cos ^{3}22.5^\circ}\right)\\
&=1-\sin ^{3}22.5^\circ\cos ^{3}22.5^\circ\left(\frac{1(\sin 67.5^\circ+\cos 67.5^\circ)}{\sin ^{3}22.5^\circ\cos ^{3}22.5^\circ}\right)\\
&=1-\frac{\sin 67.5^\circ+\cos 67.5^\circ}{\sin ^{3}22.5^\circ\cos ^{3}22.5^\circ}\\
&=1-\frac{\sin 67.5^\circ+\cos 67.5^\circ}{\left(\frac{\sqrt{2}}{2}\right)^{3}\left(\frac{\sqrt{2}}{2}\right)^{3}}\\
&=1-\frac{\sin 67.5^\circ+\cos 67.5^\circ}{\frac{1}{4}}\\
&=1-4(\sin 67.5^\circ+\cos 67.5^\circ)\\
&=1-4\left(\frac{\sqrt{2}}{2}+\frac{\sqrt{2}}{2}\right)\\
&=1-4\left(\frac{2\sqrt{2}}{2}\right)\\
&=1-4\sqrt{2}\\
&=\frac{4-4\sqrt{2}}{4}\\
&=\frac{4(1-\sqrt{2})}{4}\\
&=\frac{1-\sqrt{2}}{1}\\
&=\frac{1-\sqrt{2}}{1}\cdot\frac{1+\sqrt{2}}{1+\sqrt{2}}\\
&=\frac{1-\sqrt{2}+1+\sqrt{2}}{1+\sqrt{2}}\\
&=\frac{2}{1+\sqrt{2}}\\
&=\frac{2}{1+\sqrt{2}}\cdot\frac{1-\sqrt{2}}{1-\sqrt{2}}\\

output:
Ушбу интегрални ҳал қилмоқда, биринчи тартибдаги интеграллар қўлланилади:

∫_{}^{}х^{2}sin х^{3}dx = \frac{x^{2}}{3}sin х^{3} - \int \frac{2x}{3}cos х^{3}dx

Иккинчи интегрални ҳал қилмоқда, унинг қиймати:

∫ \frac{2x}{3}cos х^{3}dx = \frac{x}{3}cos х^{3} + \int \frac{1}{3}sin х^{3}dx

Иккинчи интегрални ҳал қилмоқда, унинг қиймати:

∫ \frac{1}{3}sin х^{3}dx = -\frac{1}{9}cos х^{3}

Интегралга қайтадан қўйиш учун, унинг қиймати:

∫_{}^{}х^{2}sin х^{3}dx = \frac{x^{2}}{3}sin х^{3} - \frac{x}{3}cos х^{3} - \frac{1}{9}cos х^{3} + C

\frac{a^2+a}{a}=\frac{a(a+1)}{a}=a+1

Сўнгра, биринчи бўлишни ikkinchi бўлишга qoldirамиз:
